		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+16" width="300" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The chart shows changes in the readership figures for three local newspapers between <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[1]</FONT> and 2001. </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
