		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="310" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">Only the Broomedge Chronicle increased its readership over the period. Between 1980 and 1990 its readership rose by <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[2]</FONT>. However, by <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[3]</FONT> the number of readers had fallen to <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[4]</FONT>. </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
