		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="310" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The Warburton Bugle also had mixed fortunes during these two decades. Starting with a readership of <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[5]</FONT> in 1980, there was a fall of 200,000 in <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[6]</FONT>. However the number of readers rose to <FONT COLOR="#0000FF">[7]</FONT> in 2001. </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="310" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
